# General

- production-ready code only
- strict TypeScript
- avoid any
- prefer explicit typing
- prefer composition over inheritance
- avoid giant files and hooks

# Naming

- interfaces start with I
- enums start with E
- global constants use UPPER_CASE

# React

- functional components only
- named exports only
- business logic outside JSX

# Architecture

- project uses FSD architecture
- src/modules is isolated from FSD
- modules may have custom internal architecture
- modules should be portable to separate libraries

# State

- Zustand for global state
- TanStack Query for server state

# Styling

- Tailwind CSS
- clsx/cva for complex variants

# Imports

- use public API
- avoid deep imports